name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Wang Biao from Jiangsu Province had myopia surgery at Aier Eye Hospital on August 11, 2022 in order to join the army. Wang Biao joined the army on September 1, 2022. More than 20 days later, he developed an eye infection and was discharged for treatment. In the end, he developed eye cancer due to long-term inflammation and infection of the eye.
On February 17, 2024, Wang Biao, who was only 25 years old, died in the hospital. On that day, his family put on military uniform for Wang Biao for the last time.
Ai Fen, director of the emergency department of Wuhan Central Hospital, who has been following this incident for a long time, questioned the matter on Weibo. She said that the state stipulates that only those with normal fundus and myopia surgery for more than half a year can join the army. She suspected that Aier Eye Hospital forged Wang Biao's myopia surgery time and diagnosis certificate.
